<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Yoann Choy ‚Äî Electrical Engineer</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;800&family=Source+Sans+3:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy:    #0d2b4e;
    --blue:    #1a5fa8;
    --sky:     #3b87d0;
    --light:   #e8f1fb;
    --white:   #ffffff;
    --slate:   #4a637f;
    --muted:   #7a93ae;
    --border:  #d0e1f0;
    --bg:      #f4f8fd;
    --text:    #0d1f30;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    overflow-x: hidden;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 200;
    background: var(--white);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 4rem;
    height: 64px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 12px rgba(13,43,78,0.06);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
  }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--blue); }

  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }

  .nav-links a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--slate);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .nav-links a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -4px; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--blue);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--blue); }
  .nav-links a:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

  /* HERO */
  #hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 400px;
    padding-top: 64px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 5rem 4rem 5rem 5rem;
  }

  .hero-right {
    background: var(--navy);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-right::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -80px; right: -80px;
    width: 320px; height: 320px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,135,208,0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-right::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -60px; left: -60px;
    width: 220px; height: 220px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,135,208,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .availability-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #4ade80;
    background: rgba(74,222,128,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.25);
    padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    width: fit-content;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
  }
  .availability-badge::before {
    content: '';
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #4ade80;
    animation: blink 1.8s ease infinite;
  }
  @keyframes blink { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0.3} }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both;
  }
  .eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    width: 28px; height: 2px;
    background: var(--blue);
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5.2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s ease both;
  }
  h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--blue); }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--slate);
    max-width: 460px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both;
  }

  .hero-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.4s ease both;
  }
  .pill {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.38rem 0.95rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--slate);
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.5s ease both;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 3px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
  }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--blue); color: var(--white); }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--navy); transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(26,95,168,0.28); }
  .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--navy); border: 1.5px solid var(--navy); }
  .btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--navy); color: var(--white); }

  /* Info cards on right */
  .info-cards {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .info-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease both;
  }
  .info-card:nth-child(1){animation-delay:0.3s}
  .info-card:nth-child(2){animation-delay:0.45s}
  .info-card:nth-child(3){animation-delay:0.6s}
  .info-card:nth-child(4){animation-delay:0.75s}

  .info-icon {
    width: 38px; height: 38px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(59,135,208,0.2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .info-icon svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; stroke: #7bbfee; fill: none; stroke-width: 1.5; }
  .info-card-label { font-size: 0.67rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38); margin-bottom: 0.18rem; }
  .info-card-value { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--white); font-weight: 300; }

  /* SECTIONS */
  .section-wrap { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5.5rem 2rem; }
  .section-header { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blue);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
  }
  .section-eyebrow::before { content: ''; width: 22px; height: 2px; background: var(--blue); }
  h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.2vw, 2.7rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 0 2rem; }

  /* ABOUT */
  #about { background: var(--white); }
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start; }
  .about-body p { color: var(--slate); font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.82; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .about-body p strong { color: var(--navy); font-weight: 600; }

  .about-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
  .stat-block { background: var(--white); padding: 1.8rem 1.4rem; text-align: center; }
  .stat-block:nth-child(3) { grid-column: span 2; }
  .stat-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue); line-height: 1; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.76rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.4; }

  /* SKILLS */
  #skills { background: var(--bg); }
  .skills-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .skill-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1.8rem;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .skill-card:hover { border-color: var(--sky); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(26,95,168,0.07); }
  .skill-card-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .skill-icon { width: 34px; height: 34px; border-radius: 6px; background: var(--light); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .skill-icon svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; stroke: var(--blue); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.5; }
  .skill-card-title { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--navy); }
  .skill-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.45rem; }
  .skill-tag { font-size: 0.77rem; padding: 0.32rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 3px; background: var(--light); color: var(--blue); }

  /* EXPERIENCE */
  #experience { background: var(--white); }
  .tl-item { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 175px 1fr; gap: 2rem; padding-bottom: 3rem; position: relative; }
  .tl-item:not(:last-child)::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 175px;
    top: 10px; bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }
  .tl-date-col { text-align: right; padding-top: 2px; }
  .tl-date { font-size: 0.73rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--blue); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .tl-location { font-size: 0.73rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.2rem; }
  .tl-body { border-left: 2px solid var(--light); padding-left: 2rem; position: relative; }
  .tl-body::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -5px; top: 5px;
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--blue);
    border: 2px solid var(--white);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--blue);
  }
  .tl-role { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
  .tl-company { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .tl-desc { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.38rem; }
  .tl-desc li { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--slate); padding-left: 1.1rem; position: relative; line-height: 1.6; }
  .tl-desc li::before { content: '‚Äì'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--muted); }

  /* PROJECTS */
  #projects { background: var(--bg); }
  .projects-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .proj-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; transition: all 0.25s; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .proj-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(13,43,78,0.1); border-color: var(--sky); }
  .proj-header {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 1.4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 88px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .proj-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -30px; right: -30px;
    width: 110px; height: 110px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,135,208,0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .proj-num { font-size: 0.64rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }
  .proj-icon { font-size: 1.7rem; z-index: 1; align-self: flex-end; }
  .proj-body { padding: 1.4rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex: 1; }
  .proj-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 0.97rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.55rem; line-height: 1.3; }
  .proj-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--slate); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; flex: 1; }
  .proj-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .proj-tag { font-size: 0.67rem; padding: 0.22rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 100px; background: var(--light); color: var(--blue); font-weight: 600; }

  /* CONTACT */
  #contact { background: var(--navy); padding: 6rem 2rem; }
  .contact-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: center; }
  .contact-left h2 { color: var(--white); font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3vw, 2.8rem); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .contact-left p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75; max-width: 380px; }
  .contact-right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.8rem; }
  .c-link {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .c-link:hover { background: rgba(59,135,208,0.15); border-color: rgba(59,135,208,0.4); color: var(--white); transform: translateX(4px); }
  .c-link svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; stroke: var(--sky); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.5; flex-shrink: 0; }

  footer {
    background: #071829;
    padding: 1.5rem 4rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.73rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }
  .anim { opacity:0; transform:translateY(18px); transition: opacity 0.65s ease, transform 0.65s ease; }
  .anim.visible { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
  .anim-d1{transition-delay:0.1s} .anim-d2{transition-delay:0.2s}
  .anim-d3{transition-delay:0.3s} .anim-d4{transition-delay:0.4s}
  .anim-d5{transition-delay:0.5s}

  /* PROFILE PHOTO */
  .profile-photo-wrap {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .profile-photo {
    width: 110px;
    height: 110px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 3px solid var(--border);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(13,43,78,0.12);
    display: block;
  }

  /* MODAL */
  .proj-card { cursor: pointer; }
  .proj-card:hover .proj-title { color: var(--blue); }

  .modal-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(13,43,78,0.55);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    z-index: 500;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.25s ease;
  }
  .modal-overlay.open {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: all;
  }

  .modal {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 6px;
    max-width: 580px;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 90vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(13,43,78,0.25);
    transform: translateY(16px) scale(0.98);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease;
  }
  .modal-overlay.open .modal { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }

  .modal-header {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 1.8rem 2rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .modal-num { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .modal-icon { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; display: block; }
  .modal-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); line-height: 1.2; }
  .modal-close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.2rem; right: 1.2rem;
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .modal-close:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: var(--white); }

  .modal-body { padding: 2rem; }
  .modal-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 340px;
    object-fit: contain;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: block;
    background: #f0f4f8;
  }
  .modal-gallery { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .gallery-img-wrap { width: 100%; }
  .gallery-controls {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
  }
  .gallery-btn {
    background: var(--light);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--navy);
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .gallery-btn:hover { background: var(--blue); color: var(--white); border-color: var(--blue); }
  .gallery-counter { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); min-width: 40px; text-align: center; }

  .modal-img-wrap { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .modal-img-caption { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .modal-section-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
  }
  .modal-section-label:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .modal-text { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--slate); line-height: 1.75; }
  .modal-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.35rem; }
  .modal-list li { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--slate); padding-left: 1.1rem; position: relative; line-height: 1.6; }
  .modal-list li::before { content: '‚Äì'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--muted); }
  .modal-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; margin-top: 0.4rem; }
  .modal-tag { font-size: 0.72rem; padding: 0.28rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 100px; background: var(--light); color: var(--blue); font-weight: 600; }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media(max-width:960px){
    nav{padding:0 1.5rem}
    .nav-links{gap:1.5rem}
    #hero{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .hero-right{display:none}
    .hero-left{padding:4rem 1.5rem}
    .section-wrap{padding:4rem 1.5rem}
    .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:3rem}
    .skills-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .projects-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
    .tl-item{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0.4rem}
    .tl-item::after{display:none}
    .tl-date-col{text-align:left}
    .contact-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:2.5rem}
    footer{flex-direction:column;gap:0.3rem;text-align:center;padding:1.5rem}
  }
  @media(max-width:640px){
    .projects-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .about-stats{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .stat-block:nth-child(3){grid-column:1}
    nav .nav-links{display:none}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">Yoann<span>.</span>Choy</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#experience">Experience</a></li>
    <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">

      <div class="modal-section-label">Overview</div>
      <p class="modal-text">${p.overview}</p>
      <div class="modal-section-label">Key Details</div>
      <ul class="modal-list">${p.details.map(d => `<li>${d}</li>`).join('')}</ul>
      <div class="modal-section-label">Outcome</div>
      <p class="modal-text">${p.outcome}</p>
      <div class="modal-section-label">Technologies</div>
      <div class="modal-tags">${p.tags.map(t => `<span class="modal-tag">${t}</span>`).join('')}</div>
    `;

    if (imgs.length > 1) {
      let current = 0;
      const imgEl = document.getElementById('galleryImg');
      const counter = document.getElementById('galleryCounter');
      document.getElementById('galleryPrev').addEventListener('click', () => {
        current = (current - 1 + imgs.length) % imgs.length;
        imgEl.src = imgs[current];
        counter.textContent = `${current + 1} / ${imgs.length}`;
      });
      document.getElementById('galleryNext').addEventListener('click', () => {
        current = (current + 1) % imgs.length;
        imgEl.src = imgs[current];
        counter.textContent = `${current + 1} / ${imgs.length}`;
      });
    }
    overlay.classList.add('open');
    document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
  }

  function closeModal() {
    overlay.classList.remove('open');
    document.body.style.overflow = '';
  }

  document.querySelectorAll('.proj-card[data-modal]').forEach(card => {
    card.addEventListener('click', () => openModal(card.dataset.modal));
    card.addEventListener('keydown', e => { if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') openModal(card.dataset.modal); });
  });

  closeBtn.addEventListener('click', closeModal);
  overlay.addEventListener('click', e => { if (e.target === overlay) closeModal(); });
  document.addEventListener('keydown', e => { if (e.key === 'Escape') closeModal(); });
</script>
</body>
</html>
